1 WHEREAS, Ginger's retirement from First Baptist Church School marks the
2 conclusion of a remarkable chapter of service, and signals the beginning of a new venture
3 through which she will continue to inspire and have a positive influence in the field of
4 education.
5 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
6 hereby commends and congratulates Ginger Gustavson upon the occasion of her retirement
7 as Head of School at First Baptist Church School in Shreveport; expresses profound
8 appreciation for decades of dedicated educational service and leadership; and extends sincere
9 and best wishes for continued happiness, success, and fulfillment in all her future endeavors.
10 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Mrs.
11 Ginger Gustavson as an expression of deep respect and appreciation.
